{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775857544676,"sessionID":"ses_286a4e46effeEb8MI420VG5SW0","part":{"id":"prt_d795baa300010X8VU75ApkGO46","messageID":"msg_d795b8f01001RCv42169fH1Qwx","sessionID":"ses_286a4e46effeEb8MI420VG5SW0","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-fd1d44801cfd47e49371896db08ed2c4","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-012/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-012/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-012 вҖ” дјҡиҜқеӯҳеӮЁжҺҘеҸЈе®ҡд№ү Tasks\n2: \n3: ## Metadata\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-012 вҖ” дјҡиҜқеӯҳеӮЁжҺҘеҸЈе®ҡд№ү |\n8: | Module | `pkg/store` |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | S |\n11: | Design | [Stage ST-0] |\n12: \n13: ---\n14: \n15: ## Task Checklist\n16: \n17: ### Phase 1: Project Setup\n18: \n19: - [ ] **T1.1** Create directory structure `pkg/store/`\n20: - [ ] **T1.2** Verify Go module exists and add dependencies if needed\n21: \n22: ### Phase 2: Core Type Definitions\n23: \n24: - [ ] **T2.1** Create `pkg/store/doc.go`\n25:   - Add package documentation\n26:   - Describe store module purpose\n27: \n28: - [ ] **T2.2** Create `pkg/store/session.go`\n29:   - Define `Session` struct with fields:\n30:     - `ID string`\n31:     - `SandboxID string`\n32:     - `Namespace string`\n33:     - `Name string`\n34:     - `Status string`\n35:     - `CreatedAt time.Time`\n36:     - `UpdatedAt time.Time`\n37:     - `ExpiresAt time.Time`\n38:     - `LastActiveAt time.Time`\n39:   - Add JSON tags for serialization\n40:   - Verify: `go build ./pkg/store/`\n41: \n42: - [ ] **T2.3** Create `pkg/store/store.go`\n43:   - Define `SessionStore` interface with methods:\n44:     - `Create(ctx, session) error`\n45:     - `Get(ctx, sessionID) (*Session, error)`\n46:     - `Update(ctx, session) error`\n47:     - `Delete(ctx, sessionID) error`\n48:     - `List(ctx, filter) ([]*Session, error)`\n49:   - Define `SessionFilter` struct for list filtering\n50:   - Verify: `go build ./pkg/store/`\n51: \n52: ### Phase 3: Error Types (Optional)\n53: \n54: - [ ] **T3.1** Define custom error types in `pkg/store/errors.go`\n55:   - `SessionNotFoundError`\n56:   - `SessionAlreadyExistsError`\n57:   - `SessionStoreError`\n58:   - Verify: `go build ./pkg/store/`\n59: \n60: ### Phase 4: Unit Tests\n61: \n62: - [ ] **T4.1** Create `pkg/store/session_test.go`\n63:   - Test Session struct JSON serialization/deserialization\n64:   - Test SessionFilter with various filter combinations\n65:   - Verify: `go test ./pkg/store/... -v`\n66: \n67: ### Phase 5: Validation & Quality\n68: \n69: - [ ] **T5.1** Run `go vet ./pkg/store/...`\n70:   - Fix any issues reported\n71: \n72: - [ ] **T5.2** Run `golangci-lint run ./pkg/store/...`\n73:   - Fix any linting issues\n74: \n75: - [ ] **T5.3** Verify JSON tags use camelCase\n76:   - Check: `sandboxId`, `createdAt`, `updatedAt`, `expiresAt`, `lastActiveAt`\n77: \n78: ---\n79: \n80: ## Task Dependencies\n81: \n82: ```\n83: T1.1 вҶ’ T1.2 вҶ’ T2.1 вҶ’ T2.2 вҶ’ T2.3 вҶ’ T3.1 вҶ’ T4.1 вҶ’ T5.1 вҶ’ T5.2 вҶ’ T5.3\n84: ```\n85: \n86: ---\n87: \n88: ## Verification Commands\n89: \n90: | Task | Verification Command |\n91: |------|----------------------|\n92: | T1.2 | `go mod tidy && go mod verify` |\n93: | T2.1-T2.3 | `go build ./pkg/store/...` |\n94: | T3.1 | `go build ./pkg/store/...` |\n95: | T4.1 | `go test ./pkg/store/... -v -cover` |\n96: | T5.1 | `go vet ./pkg/store/...` |\n97: | T5.2 | `golangci-lint run ./pkg/store/...` |\n98: \n99: ---\n100: \n101: ## Acceptance Criteria\n102: \n103: - [ ] SessionStore жҺҘеҸЈе®ҡд№үе®Ңж•ҙ\n104: - [ ] Session ж•°жҚ®з»“жһ„еҢ…еҗ«еҝ…иҰҒеӯ—ж®ө\n105: - [ ] SessionFilter ж”ҜжҢҒеҹәжң¬иҝҮж»Ө\n106: - [ ] Pass `go vet` with zero issues\n107: - [ ] Pass `golangci-lint` with zero issues\n108: - [ ] JSON tags дҪҝз”Ё camelCase\n109: - [ ] Unit tests pass\n110: \n111: ---\n112: \n113: ## Notes\n114: \n115: - д»…е®ҡд№үжҺҘеҸЈпјҢдёҚе®һзҺ°е…·дҪ“еӯҳеӮЁйҖ»иҫ‘\n116: - е…·дҪ“е®һзҺ°з”ұеҗҺз»ӯ AR жҸҗдҫӣ (еҰӮ Redis е®һзҺ°)\n117: - жҺҘеҸЈи®ҫи®ЎеҸӮиҖғ Session Manager дҪҝз”ЁеңәжҷҜ\n118: \n119: ---\n120: \n121: ## Implementation Timeline\n122: \n123: | Phase | Tasks | Status | Completion |\n124: |-------|-------|--------|------------|\n125: | Phase 1: Project Setup | T1.1-T1.2 | Not Started | 0% |\n126: | Phase 2: Core Type Definitions | T2.1-T2.3 | Not Started | 0% |\n127: | Phase 3: Error Types | T3.1 | Not Started | 0% |\n128: | Phase 4: Unit Tests | T4.1 | Not Started | 0% |\n129: | Phase 5: Validation | T5.1-T5.3 | Not Started | 0% |\n130: \n131: **Total Progress: 0% Complete**\n\n(End of file - total 131 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-012 вҖ” дјҡиҜқеӯҳеӮЁжҺҘеҸЈе®ҡд№ү Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-012 вҖ” дјҡиҜқеӯҳеӮЁжҺҘеҸЈе®ҡд№ү |\n| Module | `pkg/store` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Design | [Stage ST-0] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: Project Setup\n\n- [ ] **T1.1** Create directory structure `pkg/store/`\n- [ ] **T1.2** Verify Go module exists and add dependencies if needed","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-012/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775857544661,"end":1775857544674}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775857544679,"sessionID":"ses_286a4e46effeEb8MI420VG5SW0","part":{"id":"prt_d795bad77001EIU6deKp0g23LQ","messageID":"msg_d795b8f01001RCv42169fH1Qwx","sessionID":"ses_286a4e46effeEb8MI420VG5SW0","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-9bd9bb023d464a11832bfa8a1898ba58","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-012/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-012/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-012 вҖ” дјҡиҜқеӯҳеӮЁжҺҘеҸЈе®ҡд№ү Design\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-012 вҖ” дјҡиҜқеӯҳеӮЁжҺҘеҸЈе®ҡд№ү |\n8: | Module | `pkg/store` |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | S |\n11: | Stage | ST-1 |\n12: \n13: е®ҡд№үдјҡиҜқеӯҳеӮЁзҡ„жҠҪиұЎжҺҘеҸЈеұӮпјҢдёә Session Manager жҸҗдҫӣз»ҹдёҖзҡ„еӯҳеӮЁж“ҚдҪңжҺҘеҸЈгҖӮ\n14: \n15: ## Design\n16: \n17: ### Architecture\n18: \n19: жҺҘеҸЈи®ҫи®ЎйҒөеҫӘ Go жҺҘеҸЈжғҜдҫӢ:\n20: - ж–№жі•зӯҫеҗҚз®ҖжҙҒпјҢиҝ”еӣһ error\n21: - дҪҝз”Ё context.Context ж”ҜжҢҒи¶…ж—¶/еҸ–ж¶Ҳ\n22: - Session з»“жһ„еҸҜеәҸеҲ—еҢ–пјҢж”ҜжҢҒеӨҡз§ҚеӯҳеӮЁеҗҺз«Ҝ\n23: \n24: ### Dependencies\n25: \n26: | Package | Purpose |\n27: |---------|---------|\n28: | `context` | ж“ҚдҪңдёҠдёӢж–Ү |\n29: | `time` | ж—¶й—ҙеӯ—ж®ө |\n30: \n31: ## Data Structures\n32: \n33: ### SessionStore Interface\n34: \n35: ```go\n36: type SessionStore interface {\n37:     Create(ctx context.Context, session *Session) error\n38:     Get(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*Session, error)\n39:     Update(ctx context.Context, session *Session) error\n40:     Delete(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error\n41:     List(ctx context.Context, filter *SessionFilter) ([]*Session, error)\n42: }\n43: ```\n44: \n45: ### Session\n46: \n47: ```go\n48: type Session struct {\n49:     ID           string    `json:\"id\"`\n50:     SandboxID    string    `json:\"sandboxId\"`\n51:     Namespace    string    `json:\"namespace\"`\n52:     Name         string    `json:\"name\"`\n53:     Status       string    `json:\"status\"`\n54:     CreatedAt    time.Time `json:\"createdAt\"`\n55:     UpdatedAt    time.Time `json:\"updatedAt\"`\n56:     ExpiresAt    time.Time `json:\"expiresAt\"`\n57:     LastActiveAt time.Time `json:\"lastActiveAt\"`\n58: }\n59: ```\n60: \n61: ### SessionFilter\n62: \n63: ```go\n64: type SessionFilter struct {\n65:     Namespace string\n66:     Status    string\n67:     Name      string\n68: }\n69: ```\n70: \n71: ## API Contracts\n72: \n73: ### Create\n74: \n75: ```go\n76: func Create(ctx context.Context, session *Session) error\n77: ```\n78: - Input: Session pointer with required fields populated\n79: - Output: error on failure, nil on success\n80: \n81: ### Get\n82: \n83: ```go\n84: func Get(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*Session, error)\n85: ```\n86: - Input: sessionID string\n87: - Output: Session pointer, error (including NotFound error)\n88: \n89: ### Update\n90: \n91: ```go\n92: func Update(ctx context.Context, session *Session) error\n93: ```\n94: - Input: Session pointer with updated fields\n95: - Output: error on failure, nil on success\n96: \n97: ### Delete\n98: \n99: ```go\n100: func Delete(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error\n101: ```\n102: - Input: sessionID string\n103: - Output: error on failure, nil on success\n104: \n105: ### List\n106: \n107: ```go\n108: func List(ctx context.Context, filter *SessionFilter) ([]*Session, error)\n109: ```\n110: - Input: optional SessionFilter\n111: - Output: slice of Session pointers, error\n112: \n113: ## Error Handling\n114: \n115: е»әи®®е®ҡд№үиҮӘе®ҡд№үй”ҷиҜҜзұ»еһӢ:\n116: - `SessionNotFoundError` - дјҡиҜқдёҚеӯҳеңЁ\n117: - `SessionAlreadyExistsError` - дјҡиҜқе·ІеӯҳеңЁ\n118: - `SessionStoreError` - еӯҳеӮЁж“ҚдҪңеӨұиҙҘ\n119: \n120: ## Testing Strategy\n121: \n122: ### Unit Tests\n123: \n124: | Test Category | Coverage |\n125: |---------------|----------|\n126: | Session з»“жһ„еәҸеҲ—еҢ– | JSON еәҸеҲ—еҢ–/еҸҚеәҸеҲ—еҢ–жӯЈзЎ® |\n127: | SessionFilter иҝҮж»Ө | иҝҮж»Өеӯ—ж®өжӯЈзЎ®еҢ№й…Қ |\n128: \n129: ### Integration Tests\n130: \n131: - Mock е®һзҺ°жөӢиҜ•жҺҘеҸЈеҘ‘зәҰ\n132: - зңҹе®һеӯҳеӮЁе®һзҺ°йӘҢиҜҒ (еҗҺз»ӯе®һзҺ°жЁЎеқ—)\n133: \n134: ### Test Utilities\n135: \n136: ```go\n137: type MockSessionStore struct {\n138:     sessions map[string]*Session\n139:     // е®һзҺ°жүҖжңүжҺҘеҸЈж–№жі•\n140: }\n141: ```\n142: \n143: ## File Structure\n144: \n145: ```\n146: pkg/store/\n147:   store.go     вҖ” SessionStore жҺҘеҸЈе®ҡд№ү\n148:   session.go   вҖ” SessionгҖҒSessionFilter ж•°жҚ®з»“жһ„\n149:   doc.go       вҖ” еҢ…ж–ҮжЎЈ\n150: ```\n151: \n152: ## Open Questions\n153: \n154: - жҳҜеҗҰйңҖиҰҒж”ҜжҢҒжү№йҮҸж“ҚдҪң (BatchCreate/BatchDelete)?\n155: - жҳҜеҗҰйңҖиҰҒж”ҜжҢҒдәӢеҠЎж“ҚдҪң?\n156: - SessionFilter жҳҜеҗҰйңҖиҰҒжӣҙеӨҡиҝҮж»Өеӯ—ж®ө?\n157: \n158: ## References\n159: \n160: - еҫ…иЎҘе……\n\n(End of file - total 160 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-012 вҖ” дјҡиҜқеӯҳеӮЁжҺҘеҸЈе®ҡд№ү Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-012 вҖ” дјҡиҜқеӯҳеӮЁжҺҘеҸЈе®ҡд№ү |\n| Module | `pkg/store` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Stage | ST-1 |\n\nе®ҡд№үдјҡиҜқеӯҳеӮЁзҡ„жҠҪиұЎжҺҘеҸЈеұӮпјҢдёә Session Manager жҸҗдҫӣз»ҹдёҖзҡ„еӯҳеӮЁж“ҚдҪңжҺҘеҸЈгҖӮ\n\n## Design\n\n### Architecture\n\nжҺҘеҸЈи®ҫи®ЎйҒөеҫӘ Go жҺҘеҸЈжғҜдҫӢ:\n- ж–№жі•зӯҫеҗҚз®ҖжҙҒпјҢиҝ”еӣһ error","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-012/design.md","time":{"start":1775857544663,"end":1775857544676}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775857544682,"sessionID":"ses_286a4e46effeEb8MI420VG5SW0","part":{"id":"prt_d795ba5ab001vNEFaL10kKz16g","messageID":"msg_d795b8f01001RCv42169fH1Qwx","sessionID":"ses_286a4e46effeEb8MI420VG5SW0","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-c2816b0c9fd74f5992906d42ff2db53a","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/common/types/sandbox.go"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/common/types/sandbox.go</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: package types\n2: \n3: import (\n4: \t\"fmt\"\n5: \t\"time\"\n6: )\n7: \n8: const (\n9: \tAgentRuntimeKind    = \"AgentRuntime\"\n10: \tCodeInterpreterKind = \"CodeInterpreter\"\n11: \tSandboxKind         = \"Sandbox\"\n12: \tSandboxClaimKind    = \"SandboxClaim\"\n13: )\n14: \n15: type CreateSandboxRequest struct {\n16: \tKind      string `json:\"kind\"`\n17: \tName      string `json:\"name\"`\n18: \tNamespace string `json:\"namespace\"`\n19: }\n20: \n21: func (r *CreateSandboxRequest) Validate() error {\n22: \tif r.Kind != AgentRuntimeKind && r.Kind != CodeInterpreterKind {\n23: \t\treturn fmt.Errorf(\"kind must be %s or %s\", AgentRuntimeKind, CodeInterpreterKind)\n24: \t}\n25: \tif r.Namespace == \"\" {\n26: \t\treturn fmt.Errorf(\"namespace is required\")\n27: \t}\n28: \tif r.Name == \"\" {\n29: \t\treturn fmt.Errorf(\"name is required\")\n30: \t}\n31: \treturn nil\n32: }\n33: \n34: type CreateSandboxResponse struct {\n35: \tSessionID   string              `json:\"sessionId\"`\n36: \tSandboxID   string              `json:\"sandboxId\"`\n37: \tSandboxName string              `json:\"sandboxName\"`\n38: \tEntryPoints []SandboxEntryPoint `json:\"entryPoints\"`\n39: }\n40: \n41: type SandboxEntryPoint struct {\n42: \tPath     string `json:\"path\"`\n43: \tProtocol string `json:\"protocol\"`\n44: \tEndpoint string `json:\"endpoint\"`\n45: }\n46: \n47: type SandboxInfo struct {\n48: \tKind               string              `json:\"kind\"`\n49: \tSandboxID          string              `json:\"sandboxId\"`\n50: \tSandboxNamespace   string              `json:\"sandboxNamespace\"`\n51: \tSandboxName        string              `json:\"sandboxName\"`\n52: \tName               string              `json:\"name\"`\n53: \tSessionID          string              `json:\"sessionId\"`\n54: \tCreatedAt          time.Time           `json:\"createdAt\"`\n55: \tExpiresAt          time.Time           `json:\"expiresAt\"`\n56: \tStatus             string              `json:\"status\"`\n57: \tEntryPoints        []SandboxEntryPoint `json:\"entryPoints\"`\n58: \tUserToken          string              `json:\"userToken,omitempty\"`\n59: \tServiceAccount     string              `json:\"serviceAccount,omitempty\"`\n60: \tServiceAccountName string              `json:\"serviceAccountName,omitempty\"`\n61: \tLastActivity       time.Time           `json:\"lastActivity,omitempty\"`\n62: }\n\n(End of file - total 62 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"package types\n\nimport (\n\t\"fmt\"\n\t\"time\"\n)\n\nconst (\n\tAgentRuntimeKind    = \"AgentRuntime\"\n\tCodeInterpreterKind = \"CodeInterpreter\"\n\tSandboxKind         = \"Sandbox\"\n\tSandboxClaimKind    = \"SandboxClaim\"\n)\n\ntype CreateSandboxRequest struct {\n\tKind      string `json:\"kind\"`\n\tName      string `json:\"name\"`\n\tNamespace string `json:\"namespace\"`\n}\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/common/types/sandbox.go","time":{"start":1775857544657,"end":1775857544680}}}}
