sts pass with race detector\n- [ ] Test coverage вүҘ 80%\n- [ ] ж”ҜжҢҒ miniredis еҚ•е…ғжөӢиҜ•\n- [ ] Redis key и®ҫи®ЎеҗҲзҗҶ (session:{id}, session:expiry, session:last_activity)\n- [ ] ж”ҜжҢҒ Ping иҝһжҺҘйӘҢиҜҒ\n- [ ] ж”ҜжҢҒ ListExpiredSandboxes е’Ң ListInactiveSandboxes GC жҹҘиҜў\n- [ ] ж”ҜжҢҒ UpdateSessionLastActivity жҙ»и·ғж—¶й—ҙжӣҙж–°\n\n---\n\n## Notes\n\n- дҪҝз”Ё miniredis иҝӣиЎҢ Redis еҚ•е…ғжөӢиҜ•пјҢйҒҝе…Қдҫқиө–зңҹе®һ Redis\n- Valkey жөӢиҜ•дҪҝз”Ё mockпјҢеӣ  valkey-go дёҚжҸҗдҫӣиҪ»йҮҸзә§жөӢиҜ•е·Ҙе…·\n- Pipeline/DoMulti зЎ®дҝқ StoreSandbox е’Ң DeleteSandboxBySessionID зҡ„еҺҹеӯҗжҖ§\n- ZSET зҙўеј•и®ҫи®Ўж”ҜжҢҒй«ҳж•Ҳзҡ„иҝҮжңҹе’Ңжҙ»и·ғж—¶й—ҙжҹҘиҜў\n- еҜҶз Ғй»ҳи®Өеҝ…йңҖпјҢеҸҜйҖҡиҝҮзҺҜеўғеҸҳйҮҸзҰҒз”Ёз”ЁдәҺжң¬ең°ејҖеҸ‘\n- еҗҺз»ӯеҸҜжү©еұ•: TLS ж”ҜжҢҒгҖҒйӣҶзҫӨ hash tagsгҖҒиҝһжҺҘжұ и°ғдјҳ\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Timeline\n\n| Phase | Tasks | Status | Completion |\n|-------|-------|--------|------------|\n| Phase 1: Dependencies | T1.1-T1.4 | Not Started | 0% |\n| Phase 2: Interface & Types | T2.1-T2.5 | Not Started | 0% |\n| Phase 3: Redis Config | T3.1-T3.3 | Not Started | 0% |\n| Phase 4: Redis Methods | T4.1-T4.11 | Not Started | 0% |\n| Phase 5: Valkey Config | T5.1-T5.2 | Not Started | 0% |\n| Phase 6: Valkey Methods | T6.1-T6.10 | Not Started | 0% |\n| Phase 7: initStore | T7.1-T7.3 | Not Started | 0% |\n| Phase 8: Redis Tests | T8.1-T8.11 | Not Started | 0% |\n| Phase 9: Valkey Tests | T9.1-T9.10 | Not Started | 0% |\n| Phase 10: Config Tests | T10.1-T10.5 | Not Started | 0% |\n| Phase 11: Integration | T11.1-T11.3 | Not Started | 0% |\n| Phase 12: Validation | T12.1-T12.6 | Not Started | 0% |\n\n**Total Progress: 0% Complete**\n\n---\n\n## Key Design Decisions\n\n1. **Two Providers**: Support both Redis (go-redis/v9) and Valkey (valkey-go) for flexibility\n2. **ZSET Indexing**: Use sorted sets for expiry and activity queries (GC support)\n3. **Atomic Operations**: Pipeline (Redis) and DoMulti (Valkey) for multi-key operations\n4. **Singleton Pattern**: Single global store instance via `Storage()` function\n5. **JSON Storage**: SandboxInfo stored as JSON documents in Redis keys\n6. **Validation**: Reject invalid inputs (nil sandbox, zero expiresAt, empty sessionID)\n7. **Environment Config**: All connection parameters via env vars for 12-factor app compliance"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/common/types/sandbox.go":[{"range":{"start":{"line":60,"character":40},"end":{"line":60,"character":71}},"severity":4,"code":"default","codeDescription":{"href":"https://pkg.go.dev/golang.org/x/tools/go/analysis/passes/modernize#omitzero"},"source":"omitzero","message":"Omitempty has no effect on nested struct fields"}]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-013/tasks.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-013/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775857763801,"end":1775857763869}}}}
